data.description: Charming CITY WATER 3 bed 2 1/2 bath 2 car garage home. Centrally located in NE Palm Bay close to many amenities, shopping, Turkey Creek, and Pollak Park for easy boat ramp access. Boasting 2,334sqft all the bedrooms in the home are oversized with an on suite downstairs. The kitchen is well equipped with stainless steel appliance, tons of counter space, and a large pantry. As you walk to the privately fenced back yard you will find an expansive 11 x 50 trussed back porch!
